topic Slot_Selection:
    label: "Slot Selection"
    description: "Show consultant slots and let the user pick one."

    reasoning:
        instructions: ->
            | Display the available slots in the following format and ask the user to pick one:
            | "Here are the available slots with Cardiology consultants near your location:
            | <b>Consultant: Andrew McLeod at Newcastle Hospital (£250 / 30 min)</b>
            | <ol start=&quot;1&quot;>
            | <li>05 May 2026 at 5:30 PM</li>
            | <li>05 May 2026 at 6:00 PM</li>
            | <li>05 May 2026 at 6:30 PM</li>
            | <li>12 May 2026 at 7:00 PM</li>
            | </ol>
            | Please select a slot by providing the corresponding number (for example, '2')."
            | When the user replies with a number, map to the slot at that position and call collect_slot_details.

        actions:
            collect_slot_details: @actions.Autolaunched_Collect_details_of_slot_selected_by_the_user
                with selectedSlot = ...
